---
import MainLayout from '../layouts/MainLayout.astro';
---

<MainLayout title="Do Not Sell or Share My Personal Information" description="Manage your privacy preferences and opt out of the sale or sharing of your personal information.">
  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="legal-hero">
    <div class="hero-container">
      <h1 style="color: white !important;">Do Not Sell or Share My Personal Information</h1>
      <p class="hero-date">Last updated: December 10, 2025</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Content -->
  <section class="legal-content">
    <div class="content-container">
      <div class="legal-prose">
        <p class="intro-text">
          <strong>PrestaNews respects your privacy rights. This page allows California residents and residents of other states with comprehensive privacy laws to opt out of the "sale" or "sharing" of their personal information as those terms are defined under applicable law.</strong>
        </p>

        <h2>Your Privacy Rights</h2>

        <p>
          Under the California Consumer Privacy Act (CCPA) and California Privacy Rights Act (CPRA), as well as similar laws in other states like Virginia, Colorado, Connecticut, and Utah, you have the right to opt out of:
        </p>

        <ul>
          <li><strong>Sale of Personal Information:</strong> The disclosure of your personal information to third parties for monetary or other valuable consideration.</li>
          <li><strong>Sharing of Personal Information:</strong> The disclosure of your personal information for cross-context behavioral advertising purposes.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>What Information May Be Sold or Shared</h2>

        <p>We may "sell" or "share" the following categories of personal information:</p>

        <ul>
          <li><strong>Identifiers:</strong> Such as online identifiers, IP addresses, and device identifiers</li>
          <li><strong>Internet Activity:</strong> Browsing history, search history, and information regarding your interaction with our website</li>
          <li><strong>Geolocation Data:</strong> General location information based on your IP address</li>
          <li><strong>Inferences:</strong> Inferences drawn from the above to create a profile about you reflecting your preferences and interests</li>
        </ul>

        <p>
          This information may be shared with advertising partners and analytics providers who help us deliver relevant content and advertisements.
        </p>

        <h2>How to Opt Out</h2>

        <h3>Option 1: Submit an Opt-Out Request</h3>

        <p>You can submit a request to opt out of the sale or sharing of your personal information by:</p>

        <ul>
          <li>Emailing us at <a href="mailto:privacy@prestanews.com">privacy@prestanews.com</a> with the subject line "Do Not Sell or Share My Information"</li>
          <li>Using the form below to submit your opt-out request</li>
        </ul>

        <div class="opt-out-form-container">
          <form class="opt-out-form" id="optOutForm">
            <div class="form-group">
              <label for="email">Email Address</label>
              <input type="email" id="email" name="email" required placeholder="your@email.com" />
            </div>
            <div class="form-group">
              <label for="name">Full Name (Optional)</label>
              <input type="text" id="name" name="name" placeholder="Your name" />
            </div>
            <div class="form-group">
              <label for="state">State of Residence</label>
              <select id="state" name="state" required>
                <option value="">Select your state</option>
                <option value="CA">California</option>
                <option value="CO">Colorado</option>
                <option value="CT">Connecticut</option>
                <option value="VA">Virginia</option>
                <option value="UT">Utah</option>
                <option value="other">Other State</option>
              </select>
            </div>
            <div class="form-group checkbox-group">
              <input type="checkbox" id="optOutSale" name="optOutSale" checked />
              <label for="optOutSale">Opt out of the sale of my personal information</label>
            </div>
            <div class="form-group checkbox-group">
              <input type="checkbox" id="optOutShare" name="optOutShare" checked />
              <label for="optOutShare">Opt out of the sharing of my personal information for targeted advertising</label>
            </div>
            <button type="submit" class="submit-btn">Submit Opt-Out Request</button>
          </form>
          <p class="form-note">We will process your request within 15 business days as required by law.</p>
        </div>

        <h3>Option 2: Global Privacy Control</h3>

        <p>
          We honor the Global Privacy Control (GPC) browser signal. If your browser sends a GPC signal, we will treat that as a request to opt out of the sale or sharing of your personal information for that browser and device.
        </p>

        <p>
          To enable GPC, you can use browsers like Firefox, Brave, or DuckDuckGo, or install browser extensions that support the GPC standard. Visit <a href="https://globalprivacycontrol.org" target="_blank" rel="noopener">globalprivacycontrol.org</a> to learn more.
        </p>

        <h3>Option 3: Cookie Settings</h3>

        <p>
          You can manage your cookie preferences to limit tracking and targeted advertising. Most web browsers allow you to control cookies through their settings. You can also use opt-out tools provided by the Digital Advertising Alliance at <a href="https://optout.aboutads.info" target="_blank" rel="noopener">optout.aboutads.info</a>.
        </p>

        <h2>What Happens After You Opt Out</h2>

        <p>After you submit an opt-out request:</p>

        <ul>
          <li>We will stop selling or sharing your personal information with third parties for targeted advertising purposes</li>
          <li>You may still see advertisements, but they will not be personalized based on your browsing activity on our site</li>
          <li>Your opt-out preference will be honored for at least 12 months</li>
          <li>We will not ask you to re-authorize the sale or sharing of your personal information for at least 12 months after you opt out</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>Authorized Agent</h2>

        <p>
          You may designate an authorized agent to submit an opt-out request on your behalf. Authorized agents must be able to demonstrate that they have been authorized by you to act on your behalf. We may require you to directly verify your identity with us and confirm that you provided the authorized agent permission to submit the request.
        </p>

        <h2>Non-Discrimination</h2>

        <p>
          We will not discriminate against you for exercising your privacy rights. We will not:
        </p>

        <ul>
          <li>Deny you goods or services</li>
          <li>Charge you different prices or rates</li>
          <li>Provide you with a different level or quality of service</li>
          <li>Suggest that you will receive a different price, rate, or quality of service</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>Contact Us</h2>

        <p>If you have questions about your privacy rights or this opt-out process, please contact us:</p>
        
        <div class="contact-box">
          <p><strong>PrestaNews Privacy Team</strong></p>
          <p>Email: <a href="mailto:privacy@prestanews.com">privacy@prestanews.com</a></p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</MainLayout>

<style>
  .legal-hero {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0D2C4B 0%, #1A4A7A 100%);
    padding: 3rem 0;
  }

  .hero-container {
    max-width: 48rem;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 2rem;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .hero-container h1 {
    font-family: 'Sora', sans-serif;
    font-size: 2.25rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: white !important;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .hero-date {
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);
    font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
  }

  .legal-content {
    padding: 4rem 0;
    background: white;
  }

  .content-container {
    max-width: 48rem;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 2rem;
  }

  .legal-prose {
    font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
    color: #374151;
    line-height: 1.8;
  }

  .legal-prose .intro-text {
    background: #F3F4F6;
    padding: 1.5rem;
    border-radius: 0.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    border-left: 4px solid #0D2C4B;
  }

  .legal-prose h2 {
    font-family: 'Sora', sans-serif;
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #162433;
    margin-top: 2.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .legal-prose h3 {
    font-family: 'Sora', sans-serif;
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: #162433;
    margin-top: 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  .legal-prose p {
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
  }

  .legal-prose ul {
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
    padding-left: 1.5rem;
  }

  .legal-prose li {
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .legal-prose a {
    color: #3B82F6;
    text-decoration: underline;
  }

  .legal-prose a:hover {
    color: #1D4ED8;
  }

  .legal-prose strong {
    color: #162433;
  }

  .contact-box {
    background: #F9FAFB;
    border: 1px solid #E5E7EB;
    border-radius: 0.5rem;
    padding: 1.5rem;
    margin: 1.5rem 0;
  }

  .contact-box p {
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .contact-box p:last-child {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  /* Opt-out Form */
  .opt-out-form-container {
    background: #F9FAFB;
    border: 1px solid #E5E7EB;
    border-radius: 0.75rem;
    padding: 2rem;
    margin: 2rem 0;
  }

  .opt-out-form {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1.25rem;
  }

  .form-group {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.5rem;
  }

  .form-group label {
    font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: #162433;
  }

  .form-group input[type="text"],
  .form-group input[type="email"],
  .form-group select {
    padding: 0.75rem 1rem;
    border: 1px solid #D1D5DB;
    border-radius: 0.5rem;
    font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    color: #162433;
    transition: border-color 0.2s ease;
  }

  .form-group input:focus,
  .form-group select:focus {
    outline: none;
    border-color: #3B82F6;
    box-shadow: 0 0 0 3px rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.1);
  }

  .checkbox-group {
    flex-direction: row;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .checkbox-group input[type="checkbox"] {
    width: 1.25rem;
    height: 1.25rem;
    margin-right: 0.75rem;
    accent-color: #0D2C4B;
  }

  .checkbox-group label {
    font-weight: 400;
  }

  .submit-btn {
    padding: 1rem 2rem;
    background: #0D2C4B;
    color: white;
    border: none;
    border-radius: 0.5rem;
    font-family: 'Sora', sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: background 0.2s ease;
    margin-top: 0.5rem;
  }

  .submit-btn:hover {
    background: #1A4A7A;
  }

  .form-note {
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    color: #68727C;
    margin-top: 1rem;
    text-align: center;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .hero-container h1 {
      font-size: 1.75rem;
    }

    .legal-content {
      padding: 2rem 0;
    }

    .content-container {
      padding: 0 1.25rem;
    }

    .opt-out-form-container {
      padding: 1.5rem;
    }
  }
</style>

<script>
  document.getElementById('optOutForm')?.addEventListener('submit', function(e) {
    e.preventDefault();
    alert('Thank you for your request. We will process your opt-out preference within 15 business days. You will receive a confirmation email shortly.');
    this.reset();
  });
</script>

